*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  USER_COMMAND_EXIT  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE USER_COMMAND_EXIT INPUT.

    CASE SY-UCOMM.
    WHEN 'BACK'.

      SET SCREEN 0.
      LEAVE SCREEN.

    WHEN 'EXIT'.

      LEAVE PROGRAM.

    WHEN 'CANC'.

      SET SCREEN 0.
      LEAVE SCREEN.

  ENDCASE.

ENDMODULE.
